<p itemprop="description">A senior application operations engineer leads complex application support activities and mentors junior engineers. They design operational solutions, establish best practices, and drive improvements in application reliability and performance.</p>

<section class="role-details">
    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Lead complex application incident investigations and resolutions</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Design and implement application monitoring and observability solutions</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Mentor and guide junior application operations engineers</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Establish operational best practices and standards for applications</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Collaborate with architects on application operational requirements</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Lead application performance optimization initiatives</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Support strategic planning for application operations capabilities</li>
    </ul>
</section>

